\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12656160 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 
Oh well, you got the - you - you got the cane, you were sent to the headmaster as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 You were still caned on the hand were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12656160 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 Yes, still caned on the hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 Would you know whether or not girls were caned at this school?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12656160 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 
I never knew that because they were in another part of the building as it were. And whilst I imagined that they would - be subjected to some sort of punishment, if it was merited - I - I never knew for certain - whether they - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 For what offences would you be caned at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Queen Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12656160 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 Being late. Without good excuse or good reason. \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 work or - some damage that might - you might have done. Some bad behaviour outside. Some disobedience or - or going against instructions already given. And - oh it might have been through slipshodness - had writing or something of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 Did your parents show any more interest in your work at this school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12656160 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 Well I'm sure they were i
nterested. I'm sure they were interested, but - I don't remember that there was ever any general practice made of parents visiting the school.
