o, I don't remember that there would be any particular - effort made to serve any particular one first. I think all the plates would take it in turn according to whether it was fat or lean you see. We knew which was which in that respect you see
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 When 
