Well he'd have a high chair. He'd have a high chair, yes. And have his meal on that - for a little while.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 But even then did you still I eat together?
