\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867  somewhat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12656160 HO  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 
No I think we were - pretty much one - in that respect. We both believed in - the same things for bringing up was concerned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 Did you discuss it?
