No I don't know that we ever discussed it, it seemed to be perfectly - understood between us that - she'd had a similar bringing up to me and - we didn't seem to need to discuss that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3631299 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14818695\charrsid11217867 
